Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可以哦  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来就给“这里”上刑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,住手  那里绝对不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,就～不～住～手～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我投降  投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这也太用力了吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你自己嫌麻烦不涂防晒霜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你再轻一点嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来涂这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦喜欢纯一吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:01.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要突然问我这种事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然  要说喜不喜欢的话那当然是喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:08.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  那个  没有什么别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,喂  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦喜欢纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟也喜欢纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是  小鸟却不说出真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为朝仓君他现在很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦也很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:48.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,水越  美春还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在这样是最幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以小鸟才不说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为这样大家才都幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,那样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为必须大家每个人都幸福才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有她一个人不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样…这样…肯定是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  是爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,海边拍的照片已经冲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我交给朝仓君好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  你到我家来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎？  去朝仓君家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯一他…  正伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,实习要在外边住宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:14.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  所以现在音梦不在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后纯一他说不喜欢我做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,天天吃便利店的盒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以想让小鸟你来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,买东西的话我随时可以帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想让小鸟来做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,像以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里也好久没来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:47.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我平时不常来这家店的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  我要拿喽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,一…  二！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里也留着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这两年来的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  这昨天刚买过吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,炒面色拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,试试看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很好吃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,…就一天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,一日限定后勤部队  就再活动一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟…  嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有…回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧  朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像没人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊  是歌丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  音梦和纯一现在都出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦…不是去实习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,总之先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,那…朝仓君回来的晚吗  爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了  反正只做个色拉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？  大概是因为很久没这样做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  接下来该切黄瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？  砧板呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  放到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:30.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  菜刀在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,都换地方了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  音梦说这样用起来比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯一一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为他前一阵子还说想吃小鸟做的菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是炒面色拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  其实很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君说他已经吃上瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是先冰一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,致哥哥和爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天会稍微晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们晚饭吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,以后不要再这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟刚才还很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,来纯一家  给纯一做饭  显得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟明明喜欢纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不对纯一说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为现在这样才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:23.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟是大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,来来来  拿走拿走！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们这的头奖  巨大巧克力香蕉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,绝对要抽中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:00.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,赌上我全日本巧克力香蕉爱好者协会首任会长的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,也一定要抽中它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,（不中）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,没中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我再挑战一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,美春…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,说好了一起逛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像得花不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:26.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐去向不明  白河又说有事无论如何都脱不开身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,多点协调精神好不好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟她也？  真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,没办法  我们继续向前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想为大家做点好吃的火锅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,是苹果糖火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,又甜又酸的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,这边看来也挺费时间的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.13,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,不要随便做起生意好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊  饶了我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个主题不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐画的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,呐呐  也画画我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊～  人手不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看你挺忙的  忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知什么时候变成两人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚也不知道跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦  朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,历老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:07.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你们相处了  能帮个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,居委会的医疗站人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,再有不到一个小时  就有人来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这之前能拜托你顶一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  我不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,待会请你吃杂煎菜饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,记得是特大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:30.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:42.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊  结果又剩我一个人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟是大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,今年夏天一定得补回这两年来和朝仓君相处的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,白河小鸟是大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了  也不用叫她出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了在女孩子家的门口晃来晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,很可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个…找小鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,哎？  你不是有事出去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  已经办完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去庙会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不知什么时候变成孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,美春眼里只有香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,萌前辈当然是弄火锅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:04.54,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝看样子是要打算创下捞金鱼的世界纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可以说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:07.27,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,阿环在别人的神社帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:11.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我没有勉强你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且也已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,再见  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  我马上去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不想再骗自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我梦想的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:51.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起笑  一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你身边  感受你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你身旁  感受你的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,再往这边来点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,浴衣（一种薄和服）都打湿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:22.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:50.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚才在那边找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我还没表示这两年来的谢意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我马上去换
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,就要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没有说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为那样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有骗你  真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服的风啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:05.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,给  海边拍的照片已经洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:06.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,小鸟  音梦她去实习不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉后勤部队已经停止营业了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,再见  爱茜亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,想不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:14.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,各位～  夏天来喽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:18.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,说到夏天  那还得是火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:22.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,在耀眼的阳光照射下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:26.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,吃一口滚烫滚烫的火锅最是别有一番风味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:33.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,当中又数放了大量韭菜和红辣椒的\N「牛杂碎火锅」最有营养
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:37.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,最适合补充体力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,多吃一点  这个…
